title: Start
body:
Welcome player
So we need your help...
There are several components of the machines in our factory that are incomplete
We want you to deliver the components into the teleporter machine
But remember...
This task is'nt about speed
But it's about precision
There is no time limit in this task
We just want you to deliver the components safely
Okay that's all I want to say
Good luck
<<end>> >>
